response.overview: On February 17th GCW & VXS presents Jimmy Lloyd's All Grown Up live and exclusive on FITE+ straight from the FSW Arena in las Vegas Nevada.  Who will be, and what will happen on this birthday party? Check out below:  Mike Bailey vs Miedo Extremo East West Express vs Komander and Arez Jimmy Lloyd vs Effy  Ciclope vs Matthew Justice Dante Leon vs Cole Radrick Dark Sheik vs Santana Jackson + much more!
